        <ownedComment xmi:id="654c8c9d-88e3-459b-8746-d0bde3c2febb" body="If True, property is read only without ability to create target element. If False Property is read / write with ability to create value according to defined expressions." annotatedElement="f9809263-d129-480e-9366-dacc57904871">
